strings.Value: "This is an ominous place. Let us keep together, friends."
"Don't go too far. This place can be dangerous."
"More clerical whining. I've survived alone in worse places than this!"
"Fine by me, I love it when we sit together by the fire. And I always worry when one of us wanders off somewhere all by himself."
"I wouldn't say your company gives me any sense of safety. I think I'm going to lie down wa-a-ay over there."
"I wouldn't say your company gives me any sense of safety. I think I'm going to lie down wa-a-ay over there."
